and he broadens my mind...

783
00:31:12,136 --> 00:31:14,806
and if it's a warm night,
we go lie on the roof...

784
00:31:14,807 --> 00:31:17,342
and watch the Sputniks go by.

785
00:31:17,343 --> 00:31:18,442
Is that all?

786
