stupid little pot!

838
00:33:10,406 --> 00:33:12,532
Do you realize what you've done?

839
00:33:12,533 --> 00:33:14,658
You've ruined me, that's all.

840
00:33:14,659 --> 00:33:16,227
What are your parents
going to say?

841
00:33:16,228 --> 00:33:17,794
They trusted me,
and I trusted you.

842
00:33:17,795 --> 00:33:20,598
Then you go and pull
an idiotic stunt like this.

843
00:33:20,599 --> 00:33:23,066
Why didn't you
look after me better?

844
00:33:23,067 --> 00:33:25,937
