of you and your hot blood.

849
00:33:34,779 --> 00:33:37,373
Come in. Come in, Otto.

850
00:33:42,687 --> 00:33:44,955
This is Mr. MacNamara.

851
00:33:44,956 --> 00:33:47,825
My husband-
Otto Ludwig Piffl.

852
00:33:47,826 --> 00:33:50,692
Piffl? Wouldn't you know.

853
00:33:54,932 --> 00:33:56,634
Where did you dig him up?

854
00:33:56,635 --> 00:33:58,515
He doesn't even wear socks.

855
00:33:58,516 --> 00:34:00,395
