Because I said so.

860
00:34:11,215 --> 00:34:13,417
In Lenin's tomb,
I take my cap off.

861
00:34:13,418 --> 00:34:15,620
If Van Cliburn
plays Tchaikovsky...

862
00:34:15,621 --> 00:34:17,154
I take my cap off...

863
00:34:17,155 --> 00:34:20,324
but in Coca-Cola office, phooey!

864
00:34:20,325 --> 00:34:23,494
Do it for me,
you little darling.

865
00:34:23,495 --> 00:34:25,195
For you, I do it.

866
00:34:25,196 --> 00:34:26,897
He could use a haircut...

867
00:34:26,898 --> 00:34:28,266
and I'd like
to give it to him myself...

868
00:34:28,267 --> 00:34:29,967
with a hammer and sickle.

869
00:34:29,968 --> 00:34:30,967
Warmonger.

870
00:34:30,968 --> 00:34:31,968
Shut up, you punk.

871
00:34:31,969 --> 00:34:33,571
don't you talk like that
to my husband.

872
00:34:33,572 --> 00:34:34,638
He's not your husband!

873
00:34:34,639 --> 00:34:36,540
In the first place,
she's underage.

874
00:34:36,541 --> 00:34:39,110
Next, we don't recognize
the government of East Germany.

875
00:34:39,111 --> 00:34:41,679
