you were washing her brain!

877
00:34:43,382 --> 00:34:45,082
So the whole thing is illegal.

878
00:34:45,083 --> 00:34:47,435
No, it's not.
I have a certificate.

879
00:34:47,436 --> 00:34:49,786
And tell him
about the wedding rings.

880
00:34:49,787 --> 00:34:51,889
Forged from the steel
of a brave cannon...

881
00:34:51,890 --> 00:34:54,257
that fought at Stalingrad.

882
00:34:54,258 --> 00:34:55,660
I don't care
who your jeweler is!

883
00:34:55,661 --> 00:34:57,162
The marriage is illegal.

884
00:34:57,163 --> 00:34:58,662
You say, but in the eyes...

885
00:34:58,663 --> 00:35:00,398
of the People's Republic
of East Germany...

886
00:35:00,399 --> 00:35:01,598
we are husband and wife.

887
00:35:01,599 --> 00:35:03,133
You are not in East Germany now.

888
00:35:03,134 --> 00:35:05,236
You are in West Berlin,
and I can have you arrested...

889
00:35:05,237 --> 00:35:07,689
for Iying on rooftops
with a minor.

890
00:35:07,690 --> 00:35:10,140
Of course you can.
I know your tactics.

891
00:35:10,141 --> 00:35:12,109
You can have me arrested.
You can have tortured.

892
00:35:12,110 --> 00:35:15,113
You can have me shot like you've
been doing in the Congo!

893
00:35:15,114 --> 00:35:17,104
Africa for the Africans!

894
00:35:17,782 --> 00:35:19,583
All I want from you,
Scarlett Piffl...

895
00:35:19,584 --> 00:35:21,514
is silence
and damn little of that.

896
00:35:21,515 --> 00:35:23,444
don't you talk like that
to my wife!

897
00:35:24,522 --> 00:35:26,423
Who? Brinkley?

898
00:35:26,424 --> 00:35:28,790
Well, tell him I already
gave the message to Huntley.

899
00:35:30,895 --> 00:35:32,829
Look, Otto baby.

900
00:35:32,830 --> 00:35:34,899
If we're to live together
in peaceful coexistence...

901
00:35:34,900 --> 00:35:36,968
there must be a certain amount
of give-and-take.

902
00:35:36,969 --> 00:35:38,636
How'd you like a thousand marks?

903
00:35:38,637 --> 00:35:39,903
For what?

904
00:35:39,904 --> 00:35:41,906
Just get on your motorcycle,
go back where you came from...

905
00:35:41,907 --> 00:35:42,940
and forget
about the whole thing.

906
00:35:42,941 --> 00:35:44,709
You can't bribe him.

907
00:35:44,710 --> 00:35:45,775
Two thousand?

908
00:35:45,776 --> 00:35:46,860
How about five thousand?

909
00:35:46,861 --> 00:35:48,070
Otto, what are you saying?

910
00:35:48,071 --> 00:35:49,279
OK. Five thousand marks.

911
00:35:49,280 --> 00:35:51,649
If it's worth five thousand,
why not fifty thousand?

912
00:35:51,650 --> 00:35:53,640
Fifty thousand? You crazy?

913
00:35:54,318 --> 00:35:56,587
I just want to see
how far they will go...

914
00:35:56,588 --> 00:35:58,856
to break up a happy
Socialist marriage.

915
00:35:58,857 --> 00:36:00,475
I spit on your money.

916
00:36:00,476 --> 00:36:02,385
I spit on Fort Knox!

917
00:36:02,386 --> 00:36:04,294
I spit on Wall Street!

918
00:36:04,295 --> 00:36:06,230
Unsanitary little jerk,
isn't he?

919
00:36:06,231 --> 00:36:07,949
You and your kind are doomed.

920
00:36:07,950 --> 00:36:09,559
We will take over West Berlin.

921
00:36:09,560 --> 00:36:11,169
We will take over
Western Europe.

922
00:36:11,170 --> 00:36:12,435
We will bury you!

923
00:36:12,436 --> 00:36:15,439
Do me a favor.
Bury us, but don't marry us.

924
00:36:15,440 --> 00:36:18,875
Look at all this waste.

925
00:36:19,610 --> 00:36:23,347
Capitalism is like
a dead herring in the moonlight.

926
00:36:23,348 --> 00:36:25,749
It shines, but it stinks!

927
00:36:25,750 --> 00:36:28,685
